      <title>尽管 8 月份出现动荡，多策略对冲基金仍实现稳步增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/multistrategy-hedge-funds-notch-steady-gains-amid-august-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管全球市场受到重击且市场猜测美国可能陷入经济衰退，但 Walleye Capital 和其他多策略对冲基金上个月仍实现了稳定的回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/multistrategy-hedge-funds-notch-steady-gains-amid-august-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 12:20:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
