      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/global-borrowing-blitz-led-by-blue-chips-selling-43-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从纽约到伦敦再到东京的投资者都争相购买投资级债券，从而刺激了这些证券的大量抛售。]]></description>
